# Assets Directory

This directory contains visual assets for the Seyfr project:

## Structure
- `seyfr-hero.png` - Main hero image for README
- `screenshots/` - Application screenshots
- `logos/` - Logo files and icons

## Adding Assets
When adding screenshots or images:
1. Use descriptive filenames
2. Optimize for web (reasonable file sizes)
3. Include alt text in documentation
4. Update README.md references as needed
